---
title: Vietnamese-Style Caramelized Ginger Tofu with Savoury Veggies and Shallot Rice
description: Tonight's dinner is a  delicious ginger-forward tofu dish inspired by the the sticky, caramel-braised dishes of Vietnam.  A perfect balance of sweet and savoury, allow your taste buds to be whisked away with just a few simple steps!
